I am creating a fast-paced multiplayer Roblox arena fighting game inspired by the chaotic, close-range PvP feel of Babo Violent 2. The core gameplay is built around short, high-action matches where players spawn into a compact arena and fight each other using movement, timing, abilities, and aggressive combat mechanics. The experience should feel hectic, competitive, and easy to jump into, with constant player interaction instead of slow buildup or long downtime. The game should support a minimum of 2 players so the combat loop works, but it should feel best with several active players creating nonstop pressure, unpredictable encounters, and chaotic arena combat.
